## Further Information

Also see for further information.

* [Account Cash Transfers](#tag/Account-Cash-Transfers)
* [Account Transfer Authorizations](#tag/Account-Transfer-Authorizations)
* [Account Cash Transfer Reviews](#tag/Account-Cash-Transfer-Reviews)
* [Account Cash Totals](#tag/Account-Cash-Totals)
* [Cash Transactions](#tag/Cash-Transactions)
* [Sandbox](#tag/Sandbox)

Once an account has been created funds can be  added to an account. Funds can be quickly added in sandbox via the below endpoint without following the same steps as needed in production.

## Directly Add Funds To An Account

**Request**

```
POST v2/accounts/{{account-id}}/sandbox/fund

{
	"data" : {
		"type" : "accounts",
		"attributes" :{
			"amount" : "50000"
		}
	}
}
```

