**Request**

```
POST v2/contributions?include=funds-transfer

{
	"data" : {
		"type" : "contributions",
		"attributes" : {
			"amount" :  "500",
			"contact-id" : "{{contact-id}}",
			"funds-transfer-method-id" : "{{funds-transfer-method-id}}",
			"account-id" : "{{account-id}}"
