## Tracking a Withdrawal

The lifecycle of the disbursement request should be tracked via the corresponding [funds-transfer](#tag/Funds-Transfer). An outgoing funds-transfer needs to be verified and authorized via the [disbursement-authorization](#tag/disbursement-authorization) and all related contingent-holds also need to be cleared before the outgoing `funds-transfer` can be settled.

