Once the `disbursement-authorization` and the `contingent-holds` related to the  outgoing funds-transfer are `authorized` and `cleared` respectively then the funds-transfer can be settled as seen below in sandbox. Once a `funds-transfer` settles a corresponding [cash transaction](#tag/Cash-Transactions) will be created. If the funds-transfer is `reversed` due to return of the funds an offsetting [cash-transaction](#tag/Cash-Transactions) will be created.

**Request**

```
POST v2/funds-transfers/{{funds-transfer-outgoing-id}}/sandbox/settle
```

