The disbursement-authorization is verified via a customizable email sent to the emails listed on [contacts](#tag/Contacts) linked to the account with an `account-role` of `owner`. It can be cleared in sandbox as seen below. Generally authorization is automatic after the `disbursement-authorization` has been `owner-verified` but this depends on the [account-policy](#tag/Account-Policies), this can also be done in sandbox.

