}

// 201 Created
{
    "data": {
        "type": "resource-tokens",
        "id": "TOKEN_ID",
        "attributes": {
            ...
            "token": "{{ token to use for embed }}"
        },
        ...
    },
    ...
}
```

The token hash you use with the embedded application in available in the `resource-token-hash` attribute.

